    <who name="Sasikanth Bharadwaj">saammana</who>
    <bug_when>2014-11-17 05:39:47 -0500</bug_when>
    <thetext>The following code, when run results in a java.lang.BootstrapMethodError.

public class MyTest
{
    public static void main(String[] args)
    {
    	MyTest test = new MyTest();
    	MySupplier&lt;MyTest&gt; s = test::new;  
    }

    public interface MySupplier&lt;T&gt;
    {
        T create();
    }
}

The above code is rejected by javac because the lhs of the constructor reference isn&apos;t a class.</thetext>
  </long_desc><long_desc isprivate="0" >
